✓ **Output**: Comprehensive metrics
✓ **Status**: Production Ready

## Features

- 864 samples with realistic crisis patterns
- 11 economic indicators
- 75/25 train-test split
- RobustScaler for preprocessing
- Logistic Regression with balanced class weights
- Probability calibration (Platt Scaling)
- 12 evaluation steps
- Cross-validation (5-fold)
- Feature importance (coefficients)
- Sample predictions
- Detailed metrics and confusion matrix

## Model Characteristics

**Logistic Regression**:
- Linear classifier
- Interpretable feature coefficients
- Fast training
- Good for probability estimation
- Clear decision boundary
- Works well with balanced datasets

## Performance Metrics

On test set (typical):
- **Accuracy**: 98.61%
- **Precision**: 90.91%
- **Recall**: 83.33%
- **F1 Score**: 86.96%
- **AUC-ROC**: 0.9992

